2026-02-04 07:31:20 - StudioAtrium\Entity\Project\Files\Download:Insert {"timestamp":1770190280,"user_id":19258,"user_ip":"46.205.201.173","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/122.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Project\\Files\\Download\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\Project\\Files\\Download","entity_data":{"id":26101,"__foreign_props":[],"project_id":"1010","file_type":"sketch","user_id":19258,"name":"Ernest","surname":"Lachowicz","email":"ernimat@wp.pl","phone":"512256695","project_order_date":1,"create_date":"2026-02-04 07:31:20","status":"new","props":{"uwagi":"Chcia\u0142bym posadowi\u0107 budynek na p\u0142ycie fundamentowej. Czy jeste\u015bcie wstanie zaprojektowa\u0107 tak\u0105 p\u0142yt\u0119? Czy mo\u017cecie zrobi\u0107 ma\u0142e zmiany w projekcie jak usuni\u0119cie okna ?\r\n\r\nPozdrawiam,\r\nErnest "},"attachments":[],"_uid":6681908},"entity_changes":false}
2026-02-04 07:36:43 - StudioAtrium\Entity\User\Message:Insert {"timestamp":1770190603,"user_id":19258,"user_ip":"46.205.201.173","user_browser":"Mozilla\/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit\/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome\/122.0.0.0 Safari\/537.36","dao_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message\\DAO\\PDOMySQL","dao_event":"dao_object_insert","entity_classname":"StudioAtrium\\Entity\\User\\Message","entity_data":{"id":1479,"__foreign_props":[],"user_id":19258,"parent_id":0,"author":"Ernest","title":"Zapytanie o projekt Winston II SP Ernest Lachowicz","message":"Dzie\u0144 dobry, \r\nPodoba mi si\u0119 ten projekt, ale znalaz\u0142em jedn\u0105 dziwn\u0105 kwestie. \r\nNa zdj\u0119ciu z zewn\u0105trz na okno w kuchni wygl\u0105da jakby okap lub jaki\u015b element elewacji wchodzi\u0142 prawie w \u015bwiat\u0142o okna. Czy to jest celowy zabieg? Czy mo\u017cna to w jaki\u015b spos\u00f3b poprawi\u0107 na etapie budowy, adaptacji projektu? Czy mo\u017cna zmniejszy\u0107 wielko\u015b\u0107 okap\u00f3w bo wydaje mi si\u0119, \u017ce s\u0105 du\u017ce jak na taki parterowy budynek? \r\n\r\n\r\nPozdrawiam,\r\nErnest Lachowicz\r\ntel. 512-256-695","create_date":"2026-02-04 07:36:43","status":"new","project_id":"1010","attachments":[],"_uid":378660},"entity_changes":false}
